conversations.content: I have many items in my cart and want to clear out everything except for the electric toothbrush. Please remove the other items and place the order.

<|Function_Thought|>
The current cart contains three items: a TechBrand Wireless Mouse, a Backpack, and an Electric Toothbrush. According to the user’s request, only the Electric Toothbrush should remain in the cart. The TechBrand Wireless Mouse and the Backpack should be removed.

I will proceed to remove these two items from the cart.
<|/Function_Thought|>

<|Final_Answer|><|/Final_Answer|>

<|Function_Call|>[cart_remove_product(product_id="P001")]<|/Function_Call|>
Product ID P001 removed from cart.

<|Function_Thought|>
The TechBrand Wireless Mouse has been successfully removed from the cart. Next, I will proceed to remove the Backpack.
<|/Function_Thought|>

<|Final_Answer|><|/Final_Answer|>

<|Function_Call|>[cart_remove_product(product_id="P017")]<|/Function_Call|>
Product ID P017 removed from cart.

<|Function_Thought|>
The Backpack has been successfully removed from the cart. Now, only the Electric Toothbrush remains. I will proceed to place the order for the Electric Toothbrush.
<|/Function_Thought|>

<|Final_Answer|><|/Final_Answer|>

<|Function_Call|>[checkout_selected_cart(product_ids=["P011"], discount_code=null)]<|/Function_Call|>
